{"title":"C++高并发解决方案","uid":"4df92e277050af68278af1388258011f","slug":"C-高并发解决方案","date":"2021-07-30T03:48:58.000Z","updated":"2024-07-30T03:49:30.495Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C-高并发解决方案.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"C-高并发解决方案\"><a href=\"#C-高并发解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"C++高并发解决方案\"></a>C++高并发解决方案</h1><ol>\n<li><p>TCP+多线程 对服务器性能要求比较高</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>select（是一个文件描述符（fd）的集合，一个文件描述符对应一个客户端）对服务器性能要求比较低，是单线程在循环，并发量有限，处理效率低（循环遍历整合集合）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>epoll 理论上并发量无限，处理效率较高，不用遍历整个事件，有事件发生时直接跳过去（epoll_event结构体）集合</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>epoll+多线程 频繁启动线程浪费时间</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>epoll+线程池</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>libevent（bufferevent的集合，每个bufferevent对应一个客户端）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>libevent+多线程（和epoll+多线程不同，它不允许由多个线程来操作这个集合）</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","text":"C++高并发解决方案 TCP+多线程 对服务器性能要求比较高 select（是一个文件描述符（fd）的集合，一个文件描述符对应一个客户端）对服务器性能要求比较低...","permalink":"/post/C-高并发解决方案","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":301,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#C-%E9%AB%98%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">C++高并发解决方案</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"暗使开开","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"\\favicon.ico","link":"/","description":"<p>即使是虚拟的也会开心</p>唯有终夜长开眼，报以平生未展眉","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/344723412"},"qq":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://qm.qq.com/q/MXqKNejl6g"}}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"VScode","uid":"75d33a392d03942d61d72e896069198e","slug":"VScode","date":"2021-08-29T15:02:22.000Z","updated":"2024-07-30T01:14:35.555Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/VScode.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"VScode问题解决vscode编译 不允许使用与号(&)原因：vscode终端（terminal）默认是powershell，vscode在powershel...","permali